<paragraph id="87463686B0398807FF42FF5B9EDC7506" blockId="7.[174,1232,207,330]" pageId="7" pageNumber="478">Hosts: common eland (P = 7.9 %; I = 6.3 (2–14)), blackbuck (P = 50 %; I = 75.8 (5–183)), markhor (P = 9.1 %; I = 13); European mouflon (P = 30 %; I = 791.7 (350–1,050), Barbary sheep (P = 40 %; I = 343 (61–625)); saiga antelope (P = 13 %; I = 2.3 (2–3)).</paragraph>
